    <name>Scraterpreter</name>
    <summary>Scraterpreter is an interpreter that runs .sb3 (Scratch) projects.</summary>

    <metadata_license>MIT</metadata_license>
    <project_license>MIT</project_license>

    <description>
        <p>Scraterpreter is an interpreter that runs Scratch projects. Use Scraterpreterc to compile .sb3 (Scratch Project) files to .scrape files, then use Scraterpreter to run .scrape files.</p>
        <p>Some use-cases for Scraterpreter:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Running projects at ridiculous speeds. </li>
            <li>Providing a simple way to prototype command line programs.</li>
            <li>Allowing online judges (programming competitions) to accept Scratch programs.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For more information, visit https://github.com/scraterpreter/scrape.</p>
    </description>

